ActPilotage Act
PrecisApproval of the appointment by the Minister of Transport of YVON PAUL DUFOUR of Dartmouth, Nova Scotia, as a member of the Atlantic Pilotage Authority, to hold office during pleasure for a term of two years, in the place of John Ferguson Aspin, whose term has expired.
